{"tid":869044,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚發夢情境好真 但一扎醒就發現係虛構","createTime":"2018-10-20T04:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T06:51:14.000Z","uid":9601,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58b5261de70d80b295db0b4298e9862e19868125","tid":869044,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"訓覺發夢夢見自己同一個女性朋友一齊咗，個情境就係佢著咗件一字膊既衫同班朋友出街，啲朋友見到就起哄。我就講笑咁係背後攬住佢鎖骨同膊頭啲位，唔俾佢地睇。雖然唔係啲咩事，但個一刻我覺得好sweet，因為我夠膽係班朋友面前公開我同佢既關係，而途中亦都閃過好多拍拖既情境，當我再攬落去個刻就扎醒咗，之後個心好痛好後悔，我唔清楚個女仔係咪對我有意思，但當初我真係追佢既話唔知個結局會變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88b57d700aa1be479724c03404756533c27b5d8","tid":869044,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"你成世都唔會有女"},{"pid":"bfba10bdde1f275fd6487a3db6267a5390fc0287","tid":869044,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c88b57d700aa1be479724c03404756533c27b5d8","tid":869044,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"你成世都唔會有女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fe64931aca59682f92f8737256a3543a378f9e","tid":869044,"uid":87506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c88b57d700aa1be479724c03404756533c27b5d8","tid":869044,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"你成世都唔會有女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"caffc8b4c4888df3eda68491ef5914dddfed0de3","tid":869044,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"77fe64931aca59682f92f8737256a3543a378f9e","tid":869044,"uid":87506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c88b57d700aa1be479724c03404756533c27b5d8","tid":869044,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"你成世都唔會有女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018